Packages 
Package Description
controller
The controller package for the GizmoBall Application This package contains the controller for the application.
logging
The logging package for the GizmoBall Application This package handles the setting up of the logs
main
The main package for the GizmoBall Application where everything starts
model
The model package for the Gizmoball application The model holds the current state of the game and is responsible for updating its state during play
model.exceptions
The model.exceptions package for the GizmoBall Application This package contains all of the exceptions that are thrown by the model
model.gizmos
The model.gizmos package for the GizmoBall Application This package contains all of the gizmos that are present within the game.
tests
The tests package for the GizmoBall Application This package contains the tests for the gizmoball application.
view
The view package for the GizmoBall Application This package contains the view portion of the application
